channel.title: Cpu Speed
channel.description:
Well, I did a test at www.srtest.com to see if my pc was compatible for a game, and the result for my CPU speed was this:
Recommended: Pentium 4 or Athlon XP You Have: AMD Sempron(tm) Processor 3000+
CPU Speed Recommended: 2 Ghz You Have: 1.81 GHz Performance Rated at 3.00 GHz
Now, how the hell can a 1.81 GHz CPU be rated as 3.00 GHz? I mean, that has to be false information.
